Web Development Course for Smart Kids
by Jorge Eduardo Ardila
@digitaico

At the end of this course you’ll be able to…
    • Design, create and deploy a dynamic modern web page,  created with state of the art ES6, HTML5, CSS grid and able to consume a foreign data Api as well as able to read a local JSON dictionary.

We’ll learn…
    • What is a web page
    • Where do internet comes from
    • HTML5 → divs, tables, p, a, span, inputs, layout.
    • CSS → grid, fonts, colors, borders, tables
    • ES6 → functions, arrow functions, console, arrays, JSON objects, control structures, fetch.
    • API’s → placeholders, consumption.
    • ES6 data representation.
    • Basic DevTools
